[5/7] Hash Quality (this may take ~30s)...

=== Hash Quality ===
avalanche: % of output bits changed per input bit flip (ideal ≈ 50%)
collision: % of 1M sequential u64 inputs that collide (ideal = 0%)
chi2:      chi-squared over 256 buckets from 100K samples (ideal ≈ 255)
bit_bias:  max per-bit bias across 500K samples (ideal = 0%)

